Privacy Policy
Information We Collect
In order that you may register on EpochalStorm\'s website(s) and access the games and services provided, we collect the following personal data from you: your name and the email address that you provide.
If you visit EpochalStorm.com from certain other websites, such as facebook.com, we may also record your ID for those websites.
Security
We use standard and reasonable technological and procedural measures to protect the information you provide. However, the Internet is an open system and we cannot guarantee that unauthorized third parties will never be able to defeat those measures or use your personal information for improper purposes.
Changes to this Privacy Policy
If our privacy policy changes in any way, we will place an updated version on our website. Review this policy regularly to ensure that you are always aware of what information we collect, how we use it and under what circumstances, if any, we will share it with other parties.
